    Design a mobile-first “Offers For You” section for a premium jewelry brand Velonna, with interactive expandable behavior and multiple UI states.
    
    ⚠️ Important instruction:
    Keep the entire design, layout, spacing, typography, and behavior EXACTLY the same as provided.
    Do not change anything except the icon color.
    
    🎨 Icon Styling Update (Only Change Required)
    All icons (tag/discount icons and any UI icons) must be changed from black to:
    Soft pink / rose color (#e06a7a)
    Maintain same icon style, size, stroke, and placement
    Do NOT modify icon shape or layout
    🧩 Header Section
    Title: “Offers For You”
    Subtitle: “(Can be applied at checkout)”
    📦 Default State (Collapsed View)
    Show only 2 offer cards
    Display “+4 more offers” below
    📦 Expanded State
    Clicking “+4 more offers” reveals all offers
    🎴 Offer Cards
    Same layout and structure as provided
    Arrow toggle behavior unchanged
    🔄 Accordion Behavior
    Same expand/collapse interaction
    Same animation and rotation
    🎯 Interactions
    Copy code behavior unchanged
    🧾 Footer
    Same “Close” button behavior
    🎨 Design Rules
    Keep everything exactly the same
    DO NOT modify spacing, fonts, layout, or structure
    ONLY update icon color to #e06a7a (soft pink)
    💎 Final Output Requirement
    
    The UI should look identical to the original design, with the only visible difference being pink icons instead of black, maintaining a premium jewelry brand aesthetic., Design a mobile-first “Offers For You” section for a premium jewelry brand Velonna, with interactive expandable offer cards.
    
    ⚠️ Important:
    Keep the existing UI, layout, spacing, typography, and styling EXACTLY the same.
    Do NOT redesign anything. Only fix functionality and visibility issues.
    
    🔴 Critical Fix Required (Main Issue)
    When a user clicks the arrow icon, the offer card must expand
    On expansion, the following MUST be visible:
    Coupon code (e.g., SAVE10 / VELONNA15)
    “Copy Code” button
    
    ✅ The coupon code MUST NOT be hidden
    ✅ It must be clearly visible inside the expanded section
    
    🎴 Offer Card Behavior (Accordion)
    
    Each card must have 2 states:
    
    🔹 Closed State:
    Show:
    Icon (pink color #e06a7a)
    Offer title/description
    Arrow (downward)
    Hide:
    Coupon code
    Copy button
    🔹 Open State (on click):
    Show:
    Coupon code (styled pill or bold text like “SAVE10”)
    “Copy Code” button
    Arrow rotates upward
    Smooth expand animation
    🧪 Visibility Rules (VERY IMPORTANT)
    Coupon code section must NOT have:
    display: none when open
    opacity: 0
    visibility: hidden
    Ensure proper class toggle like:
    .active or .open state
    Expanded content must be rendered inside DOM correctly
    🎯 Copy Code Functionality
    Clicking “Copy Code” should:
    Copy coupon to clipboard
    Show feedback → “Copied!”
    🎨 Icon Styling
    All icons must be soft pink (#e06a7a)
    Do NOT use black icons
    📦 Offer List Behavior
    Default:
    Show only 2 offers
    Show “+4 more offers”
    On Click:
    Reveal all offers
    🧾 Footer
    “Close” button collapses list back to 2 offers
    🚨 Expected Final Behavior
    Clicking arrow → expands card
    Coupon code becomes visible
    Copy button works
    Clicking again → collapses
    💎 Final Requirement
    
    The UI should look identical to the current design, but with:
    
    ✅ Coupon codes visible on expand
    ✅ Fully working accordion
    ✅ Pink icons
    ❌ No layout or style changes, Design a mobile-first “Offers For You” section for a premium jewelry brand Velonna, maintaining the existing UI and layout exactly as is.
    
    ⚠️ Important:
    Do NOT change layout, spacing, typography, or structure.
    Only apply the following 2 fixes.
    
    🔴 Fix 1: Coupon Code Styling
    The coupon code (e.g., SAVE10, VELONNA15) must be displayed inside a pink bordered box
    Style requirements:
    Border: 1.5px solid #e06a7a
    Text color: #e06a7a
    Background: transparent or very light pink
    Padding: 6px 12px
    Border-radius: 6–8px
    Font-weight: medium or semi-bold
    The box should look clean and minimal (not filled dark like button)
    🔴 Fix 2: Remove Unwanted Text
    Remove the extra descriptive text shown above the “Copy Code” button:
    Example: “Valid on minimum purchase…”
    Example: “Cannot be combined…”
    
    ❌ This text must NOT be visible
    ❌ Do not leave empty spacing
    
    🎴 Final Expanded Card Layout
    
    When a card is opened, it should show ONLY:
    
    Coupon code (pink bordered box)
    “Copy Code” button below or aligned right
    
    No extra descriptions or helper text
    
    🎨 Keep Everything Else Same
    Pink icons (#e06a7a)
    Accordion behavior
    Spacing and layout
    Button styles
    💎 Final Output Requirement
    
    The UI should look identical to the current version, except:
    
    ✅ Coupon code appears in a pink outlined box
    ❌ No extra descriptive text above copy button
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-offers-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: 20px 16px;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
  }

  .ai-offers-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ai-offers-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-offers-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .ai-offers-list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-offer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-offer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-offer-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-offer-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-offer-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .ai-offer-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    stroke: #e06a7a;
    fill: none;
  }

  .ai-offer-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-offer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.code_color }};
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-offer-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-offer-toggle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .ai-offer-toggle-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.arrow_color }};
    fill: none;
  }

  .ai-offer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.expanded .ai-offer-toggle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .ai-offer-details-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-offer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.expanded .ai-offer-details-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .ai-offer-details-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0 16px 14px 48px;
  }

  .ai-offer-code-display-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: #e06a7a;
    border: 1.5px solid #e06a7a;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 7px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .ai-offer-copy-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.copy_button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.copy_button_text }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.copy_button_border }};
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-offer-copy-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.copy_button_hover_bg }};
  }

  .ai-offer-copy-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    stroke: currentColor;
    fill: none;
  }

  .ai-offer-copy-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}.copied {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.copied_button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.copied_button_text }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.copied_button_border }};
  }

  .ai-show-more-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-show-more-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: {{ block.settings.show_more_color }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.show_more_border }};
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-show-more-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.show_more_hover_bg }};
  }

  .ai-show-more-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}.hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-offers-footer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-close-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.close_btn_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.close_btn_text }};
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-close-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.close_btn_hover_bg }};
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-offers-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }

    .ai-offers-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .ai-offer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<offers-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-offers-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-offers-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <h2 class="ai-offers-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</h2>
    <p class="ai-offers-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subtitle }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ai-offers-list-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% for i in (1..6) %}
      {% liquid
        assign enabled_key = 'offer_' | append: i | append: '_enabled'
        assign code_key = 'offer_' | append: i | append: '_code'
        assign description_key = 'offer_' | append: i | append: '_description'

        assign enabled = block.settings[enabled_key]
        assign code = block.settings[code_key]
        assign description = block.settings[description_key]
      %}

      {% if enabled and code != blank %}
        <div class="ai-offer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {% if i > 2 %}hidden{% endif %}" data-offer-index="{{ i }}">
          <div class="ai-offer-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-offer-left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-offer-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"></path>
                  <line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"></line>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-offer-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if description != blank %}
                  <p class="ai-offer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ description }}</p>
                {% else %}
                  <p class="ai-offer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ code }}</p>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ai-offer-toggle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-offer-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-offer-details-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-offer-code-display-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ code }}</div>
              <button class="ai-offer-copy-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-code="{{ code }}">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                  <path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="copy-text">Copy Code</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="ai-show-more-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <button class="ai-show-more-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <span class="show-more-text">+4 more offers</span>
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="ai-offers-footer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <button class="ai-close-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.close_btn_label }}</button>
  </div>
</offers-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class OffersSection{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.cards = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-offer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.showMoreBtn = this.querySelector('.ai-show-more-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.showMoreText = this.showMoreBtn.querySelector('.show-more-text');
        this.closeBtn = this.querySelector('.ai-close-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.isExpanded = false;
        this.visibleCount = 0;
        this.totalCount = 0;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.countOffers();
        this.setupEventListeners();
        this.updateShowMoreButton();
      }

      countOffers() {
        this.cards.forEach((card) => {
          this.totalCount++;
          if (!card.classList.contains('hidden')) {
            this.visibleCount++;
          }
        });
      }

      setupEventListeners() {
        this.cards.forEach((card) => {
          const header = card.querySelector('.ai-offer-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          const copyBtn = card.querySelector('.ai-offer-copy-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

          header.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            if (!e.target.closest('.ai-offer-copy-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}')) {
              this.toggleCard(card);
            }
          });

          if (copyBtn) {
            copyBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
              e.stopPropagation();
              this.copyCode(copyBtn);
            });
          }
        });

        if (this.showMoreBtn) {
          this.showMoreBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            this.toggleShowMore();
          });
        }

        if (this.closeBtn) {
          this.closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            this.closeOffers();
          });
        }
      }

      toggleCard(card) {
        const wasExpanded = card.classList.contains('expanded');
        
        this.cards.forEach((c) => {
          c.classList.remove('expanded');
        });

        if (!wasExpanded) {
          card.classList.add('expanded');
        }
      }

      toggleShowMore() {
        this.isExpanded = !this.isExpanded;

        if (this.isExpanded) {
          this.cards.forEach((card) => {
            card.classList.remove('hidden');
          });
          this.showMoreText.textContent = 'Show less';
        } else {
          this.cards.forEach((card, index) => {
            if (index >= 2) {
              card.classList.add('hidden');
              card.classList.remove('expanded');
            }
          });
          this.showMoreText.textContent = '+4 more offers';
        }
      }

      updateShowMoreButton() {
        if (this.totalCount <= 2) {
          this.showMoreBtn.classList.add('hidden');
        }
      }

      copyCode(button) {
        const code = button.getAttribute('data-code');
        const copyText = button.querySelector('.copy-text');
        
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(code).then(() => {
          button.classList.add('copied');
          copyText.textContent = 'Copied!';
          
          setTimeout(() => {
            button.classList.remove('copied');
            copyText.textContent = 'Copy Code';
          }, 2000);
        }).catch(() => {
          const textArea = document.createElement('textarea');
          textArea.value = code;
          textArea.style.position = 'fixed';
          textArea.style.left = '-999999px';
          document.body.appendChild(textArea);
          textArea.select();
          
          try {
            document.execCommand('copy');
            button.classList.add('copied');
            copyText.textContent = 'Copied!';
            
            setTimeout(() => {
              button.classList.remove('copied');
              copyText.textContent = 'Copy Code';
            }, 2000);
          } catch (err) {
            console.error('Failed to copy code');
          }
          
          document.body.removeChild(textArea);
        });
      }

      closeOffers() {
        this.isExpanded = false;
        this.cards.forEach((card, index) => {
          if (index >= 2) {
            card.classList.add('hidden');
            card.classList.remove('expanded');
          }
        });
        this.showMoreText.textContent = '+4 more offers';
      }
    }

    customElements.define('offers-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}', OffersSection{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

